#248;pe v&#229;r l&#229;sbare&#160;<a href=\"https://www.defa.com/no/produkt/econnect-docking-type-2/\">eConnect Docking enhet</a>&#160;som beskytter din kabel fra tyveri, samtidig som den gj&#248;r den enkel &#229; lagre og beskytter pluggen p&#229; ladestasjonsiden fra fukt og st&#248;v. Kj&#248;per du ogs&#229; med en <a href=\"https://www.defa.com/no/produkt/econnect-premium-bag-mode-3/\">eConnect Premium Cable Bag</a>&#160;f&#229;r du en praktisk og solid bag til &#229; ha din Mode 3 ladekabel i under transport. Om du &#248;nsker et enklere alternativ kan du ogs&#229; velge v&#229;r <a href=\"https://www.defa.com/no/produkt/econnect-basic-bag-mode-3/\">Basic Bag</a> til &#229; oppbevare din kabel.</p>\n<p>Lurer du p&#229; hvilken type ladekabel du trenger til din bil?</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #cc0000\"><strong><a style=\"color: #cc0000\" href=\"https://www.defa.com/no/elbil-ladekabel-guide-velg-kabel-for-ditt-behov/\">Les v&#229;r guide til ladekabler her!</a></strong></span></p>\n	</div>\n\n</div>', 'https://www.defa.com/no/produkt/econnect-elbil-ladekabel-mode-3-138kw/', ', https://www.defa.com/content/uploads/Images/EV-Charging/Charging-cables/1000x1000/Type-2-plug-male-female-coiled-velcro.jpg, https://www.defa.com/content/uploads/Images/EV-Charging/Charging-cables/1000x1000/Cap.collage-branded.jpg, https://www.defa.com/content/uploads/Images/EV-Charging/Charging-cables/1000x1000/eConnect_IQ_width_cable_connected_cap_snow_2750_web-10001000.jpg, https://www.defa.com/content/uploads/Images/EV-Charging/Charging-cables/1000x1000/eConnect_width_cable_wall_winter_2666_web-10001000.jpg, https://www.defa.com/content/uploads/Images/EV-Charging/Charging-cables/1000x1000/eConnect_IQ_width_lady_hand_connecting_car_winter_2344_web-10001000.jpg, https://www.defa.com/content/uploads/Unorganized/eConnect_plug_car_width_TE_DEFA_MG_8425_WEB_1000x1000.png, https://www.defa.com/content/uploads/Images/EV-Charging/Charging-cables/1000x1000/19119_DEFA_Econnect_ONLINES-v002.00